12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 3A O.S. 2021, Section 267, is
14 amended to read as follows:
15 Section 267. For purposes of this act, the organization elected
16 by horsemen that was, in 2003, providing representation for
17 participating Thoroughbred horsemen at meets restricted to
18 Thoroughbred horses only shall be the official representative of all
19 Thoroughbreds participating in live race meets conducted by an
20 organization licensee. The organization elected by horsemen that
21 was, in 2003, providing representation for the breeds participating
22 in mixed-breed racing shall be the official representative of all
23 non-Thoroughbreds participating in live race meets conducted by an
24 organization licensee.
